            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%2025%3A1-28%3A13%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPraise%20for%20Judgment%20and%20Salvation%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20I%20will%20honor%20and%20praise%20your%20name%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20you%20are%20my%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYou%20do%20such%20wonderful%20things!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYou%20planned%20them%20long%20ago%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20now%20you%20have%20accomplished%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20turn%20mighty%20cities%20into%20heaps%20of%20ruins.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ECities%20with%20strong%20walls%20are%20turned%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBeautiful%20palaces%20in%20distant%20lands%20disappear%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20will%20never%20be%20rebuilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20strong%20nations%20will%20declare%20your%20glory%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eruthless%20nations%20will%20fear%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%20are%20a%20tower%20of%20refuge%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ea%20tower%20of%20refuge%20to%20the%20needy%20in%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYou%20are%20a%20refuge%20from%20the%20storm%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20a%20shelter%20from%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFor%20the%20oppressive%20acts%20of%20ruthless%20people%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eare%20like%20a%20storm%20beating%20against%20a%20wall%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3Eor%20like%20the%20relentless%20heat%20of%20the%20desert.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBut%20you%20silence%20the%20roar%20of%20foreign%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAs%20the%20shade%20of%20a%20cloud%20cools%20relentless%20heat%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20the%20boastful%20songs%20of%20ruthless%20people%20are%20stilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20Jerusalem%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E25%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EOn%20this%20mountain%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2025%3A10.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewill%20spread%20a%20wonderful%20feast%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20all%20the%20people%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIt%20will%20be%20a%20delicious%20banquet%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewith%20clear%2C%20well-aged%20wine%20and%20choice%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_7%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20he%20will%20remove%20the%20cloud%20of%20gloom%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20shadow%20of%20death%20that%20hangs%20over%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_8%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20swallow%20up%20death%20forever!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20wipe%20away%20all%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20will%20remove%20forever%20all%20insults%20and%20mockery%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eagainst%20his%20land%20and%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20spoken!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_9%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20that%20day%20the%20people%20will%20proclaim%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20our%20God!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWe%20trusted%20in%20him%2C%20and%20he%20saved%20us!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThis%20is%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20in%20whom%20we%20trusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ELet%20us%20rejoice%20in%20the%20salvation%20he%20brings!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_25_10%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%